00:36:04.640 --> 00:36:09.440
They say there are two kinds
of writers-- the plotters

00:36:09.440 --> 00:36:11.264
and the pantsers, right?

00:36:11.264 --> 00:36:13.680
Plotters work everything out
in an outline format and say,

00:36:13.680 --> 00:36:14.460
this is what's going to happen.

00:36:14.460 --> 00:36:16.880
Pantsers are like, eh,
let's just see what happens.

00:36:16.880 --> 00:36:18.910
And I'm the latter, for sure.

00:36:18.910 --> 00:36:21.055
So at the end, I
had this in my mind

00:36:21.055 --> 00:36:22.930
the whole time I'm
writing the book is here's

00:36:22.930 --> 00:36:23.950
